metadata.title: Tissot PRS 516 Chronograph Automatic Mens Watch T1004273620100
features: Featuring a Black Band, Black PVD Case, Scratch Resistant Sapphire Crystal
description: Black Carbon dial enhanced by luminous black paddle-style hands. Black PVD stainless steel case with a black leather band. Automatic movement. 100 meters / 330 feet water resistance. Fixed bezel. Scratch Resistant Sapphire crystal. Skeleton caseback. Butterfly clasp. Pull / Push crown. Case size 45 mm x 15.85 mm. Band 21 mm x long. Tissot T100.427.36.201.00 PRS 516 Watch.
